folder: Tillary St. & Gold St., Brooklyn, NY
text:
185-187 Tillary Street, north side, between Gold and Prince Streets.

July 1, 1934.

P. L. Sperr.

folder: Tillary St. & Gold St., Brooklyn, NY
text:
Tillary Street, east from Flatbush Avenue Extention. The area in the center, which was formerly the north side of Tillary street, was cleared of all its buildings in connection with the proposes construction of Fort Greene Houses.

View 2 shows the south side of the street only, seen across Flatbush Avenue Extention.

P. L. Sperr

Views 1,2: August 23, 1939
